cast.overview: South Africa, 1978. Tim Jenkin and Stephen Lee, two white political activists from the African National Congress imprisoned by the apartheid regime, put a plan in motion to escape from the infamous Pretoria Prison.
cast.title: Escape from Pretoria

details.biography: Michelle Nightingale is a highly sought after vocalist, actress and presenter. A seasoned performer, her experiences range from corporate events to cabaret to leading roles in musicals. Her voice has a clarity and beauty all her own and combined with a naturally warm and effervescent personality.
details.name: Michelle Nightingale
